arabic.title: Arrabny leek
text: arrabny liek me7tag a7ess ennak m3aya
me7tag le alb yekhaf 3alaya yedommeny
sadda2ny liek gowaya shoo2 maloosh nhaya
we 7aneeny liek 3ammal yakhodny yesheddeny
khalleik dayman m3aya ana ebtadeet ayamay biek
we m3ak ana le elnhaya we ganb minnak bien edeek
ya 7abeeb alby we 7abeeb rou7y ana me7tag eliek
e7sasy biek ya 7abeeby khadny le donia 3omry ma 3eshtha
we kol marra tkoon m3aya kol 7aga ba7ebbha
bien edaya edeek we khodny ngheeb 3an elnas kollha
ninsa elly ra7 binna zaman we n3eesh 7kaya

english.title: Arrabny leek
text: Bring me closer to you, I need to feel you with me
I'm in need for a heart that worries for me and will hold me
Believe me, inside me there is a passion for you, to which there is no end
And my affection for you pulls me closer to you
Stay with me always, I've started my days with you
I'm with you til the end, I am beside you and between your arms
My sweetheart, my soul mate, I need you
My feelings for you have taken me to a world I hadn't seen before
Whenever you're with me I love everything around me
In my hands are your hands and take me, let's disappear away from all the people
Forget the past that we had lived and live a fairytale
